Multi-talented actress, Funke Akindele-Bello, has celebrated her Oscars membership. The actress took to her Instagram story to celebrate the landmark. Academy of Motion Pictures Art and Science, otherwise known as Oscars, invited the actress to join its membership class of 2022. She is among the 397 artiste and executives invited by the organisation for its membership selection. This development happened amidst the collapse of her marriage to her husband, Abdulrasheed Bello, aka JJC Skillz. However, the actress has decided to keep sealed lips about the end of her six-year-old union to her husband. Despite the series of mixed reactions trailing the end of the marriage, the mother of two has chosen to look the other way as if nothing has happened to her marriage. The actress has decided to shut her ears to happenings around her, but she is concentrating on her children and career.